title: IT Support
description: We work in partnership with you to fulfill all your IT needs in Kelowna, the Okanagan and across southern BC.<!-- excerpt --> We treat your network as if it were our own, so you can rest assured that it will be safe, secure and running as efficiently as possible.

sections.heading: Partner
sections.text: With us as your IT partner, you won't have to rely on Bob who "knows a lot about computers" to figure things out. You'll have a pro-active, virtual IT department monitoring your entire network, and often resolving issues before you know they exist. And whenever possible, we'll work on your hardware and software outside regular business hours to minimize disruptions to your work day.

sections.heading: Security
sections.text: Hackers are working 24/7 to break into any network they can, including yours. We'll minimize the threat by making sure you have the right equipment and that it's always updated to keep the bad guys out. Furthermore, our regular maintenance will ensure your Windows servers and computers are kept up to date to guard against known vulnerabilities. We'll also monitor your computers for unwanted software and uninstall it.

sections.heading: Support
sections.text: More than ever, businesses rely on technology for almost everything they do. Not suprisingly, when that technology stops working, all too often so does the business. And when time is money, down-time can cost. A lot. Our goal is to make sure down-time doesn't happen. But if it does, we'll drop everything to support you and get things up and running again ASAP. So, lean on us. We're here for you 24/7/365.
